{"tid":599597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好忙喎】邊揭護照邊碌FB 入境處女職員咁樣開工被處分","createTime":"2018-03-20T14:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T21:18:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba7211af1b893abab332c7d3b7ded8ee717d7bb","tid":599597,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"即時國際  2018-03-20 11:33:15 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n南非一名入境處女職員，在櫃位當值時將電話放在辦公桌上玩Facebook渾然忘我，醜態被遊客全數拍下。<br />\n<br />\n片段是在津巴布韋馬塔貝萊蘭省（Matabeleland）貝特橋鎮（Beitbridge）一個邊境檢查站拍攝，女職員是南非入境處的人員。<br />\n<br />\n由長約1分半鐘的片段所見，女職員一邊看着屏幕上的Facebook，一邊翻閱護照，雖然她的目光一度轉回護照上，但明確看得出她心思不在此。漫不經心地把護照翻閱了足足20秒，女職員終於肯往護照上蓋印，然後目光又馬上回到手機上。<br />\n<br />\n女職員一邊操作Facebook，一邊接過另一本護照，今次她索性先把護照放到一邊，先欣賞Facebook上的照片，只見她看得非常認真，把螢幕拉上又拉落，大約15秒後才看完。女職員未有收手，趁打開訊息的空閒時終拿起護照，一時手滑幾乎把護照都丟了，她整個人馬上彈起，之後故作鎮定望向一邊。女職員的雙眼始終緊盯手機屏幕，她之後施施然往電腦輸入資料，隨便打開護照一頁就往上蓋印。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南非內政部長吉加巴（Malusi Gigaba）譴責女職員在處理保安文件時不專心，並下令對她紀律處分，他說：「部門政策嚴禁前線辦公室人員，在執行職務時使用手機。這名職員已被查明身份，事件將會進入內部紀律程序。」女職員當值當日，3名值勤主管亦因監管不力而要接受紀律處分。"},{"pid":"c280a1f9b4ffc3582e9e95206a99abde1b57fb02","tid":599597,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180320/57959257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57959257&d=al32BsPKWMQRvAALuvaY6gKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=f2ac953a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57959257&h=6c867560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180320/57959257</a>"},{"pid":"23883a4a127d190f5f6e9c6e9ac6d2e63d12f0c4","tid":599597,"uid":155404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"邊揭護照邊碌FB 入境<span style=\"color: red;\">處女</span>職員咁樣開工被處分"},{"pid":"f7c4eb716ba67cb584921b7fc0c3ac8d2c99e90d","tid":599597,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T20:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651a1c584d119e8ea475397baf123c84051edca3","tid":599597,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T20:29:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95b1ed621e146dc0e2acdb7510812ed4bbbaf83d","tid":599597,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926ec798c10de147d369306012e21177a0466cd9","tid":599597,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T21:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}